17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
18 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
19 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 509.7 of Title 57, unless there
20 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
21 A. For purposes of this section:
22 1. “Changing room” means a room or area in which a person may
23 be in a state of undress while in the presence of others, including
24 a locker room or shower room;
